# Frontend Environment Variables

# The WebSocket URL for real-time agent activity feed.
# For local development, this can be left blank (it defaults to ws://localhost:3001/ws/feed).
# For production, uncomment and set this to your deployed API URL:
# VITE_WS_URL=wss://api.codeward.com/ws/feed

# The REST API URL
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.codeward.com
